    <title>Dear-Sir论文阅读笔记</title>
    <url>/2021/05/18/Dear-Sir%E8%AE%BA%E6%96%87%E9%98%85%E8%AF%BB%E7%AC%94%E8%AE%B0/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p><em>Dear Sir or Madam, May I Introduce the GYAFC Dataset: Corpus, Benchmarks and Metrics for Formality Style Transfer</em></p>
<span id="more"></span>
<h3 id="%E4%B8%BB%E8%A6%81%E8%B4%A1%E7%8C%AE" id="主要贡献">主要贡献</h3>
<ul>
<li>
<p>GYAFC数据集</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Benchmark：受启发于Low source MT，PBMT和NMT</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Metrixs：评价指标</p>
<ul>
<li>formality</li>
<li>fluency</li>
<li>meaning preservation</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<h3 id="gyafc-%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E9%9B%86" id="GYAFC-数据集">GYAFC 数据集</h3>
<p>来源：Yahoo Answers L6 corpus</p>
<p><img src="Figure2.png" alt="1" /></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p>预处理数据集</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>训练分类器：-3 (very informal) to 3 (very formal) PT16</p>
<ul>
<li>5000条人工标注数据from L6</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>
<p>选取E&amp;M和F&amp;R领域</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p><img src="Table3.png" alt="2" /></p>
<ul>
<li>使用训练集，双向训练风格迁移模型</li>
<li>每一个方向的原数据都有3种不同的改写</li>
</ul>
<pre class="mermaid">graph TD;
    A-->B;
    A-->C;
    B-->D;
    C-->D;</pre>
<h4 id="%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90" id="分析">分析</h4>
<ul>
<li>edit distance (<em>Levenshtein</em> Distance)</li>
<li>formality score
<ul>
<li>分类器</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>定量分析：
<ul>
<li>phrasal paraphrases (47%)</li>
<li>edits to punctuations (40%)</li>
<li>expansion of contractions (12%).</li>
<li>capitalization (46%) and normalization (10%)</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
]]></content>
